quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  71,21,"Nooe a re: “Mong`a ka! Ruri! ba ntatotse, eaba ba sala morao batho bao thepa le bana ba bona li sa tl’ong ho ba thusa ka letho haese Tahleho"
  71,22,“Ba lohile leqheka le ts’abehang
  71,23,"“Ba re: “Le se lahle melingoana ea lona kherehloa. E leng Wadd kapa Suw’a, le haele Yaghuth, Ya’uq kapa Nasr"
  71,24,"Ruri! Ba khelositse batho ba bangata tseleng, uena ha ho kamoo u ka putsang baetsalibe kateng haese ka ho kheloha.”"
  71,25,"Ba ile ba khamisoa metsi ho latela libe tsa bona, eaba ba akheloa Mollong. Ha ho bathusi ba ileng ba ba fumana ntle ho Allah"
  71,26,"Nooe a re: “Mong`a ka! U se siee leha e le moneketsela feela oa moetsalibe lefats’eng"
  71,27,"Hobane haeba U ka ba siea, ba tla khelosa makhabunyane a Hau le tsoala tsa bona e tla ba baetsalibe"
  71,28,"Mong`a ka! U nts’oarele ‘moho le batsoali ba ka le ba-kholoang bohle ba keneng lelapeng la ka, banna le basali, U se ke oa putsa baetsalibe ka letho haese timelo"